,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgyuWVCMRpv6vHVlkn94AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"Andromeda","like_count":0,"author_id":"UCzOOTh4GYVno-IJAn2fMVHA","author":"@ManateeCrab","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_lp0KE3Typatg8G3GfqTXi-jw14JNWHB3pCvC3WDfdSlBo=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@ManateeCrab","is_favorited":false,"timestamp":1398556800,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgzfMJYLAnDPB_QiRet4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"who was the composer?","like_count":0,"author_id":"UCHWcF-H2MeqWj0BHaCPkdWA","author":"@Hazztech","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_mW3ny8y6Czoaxoj-YDyyhsnTp9qgDGVFFtraXHJS6A_Q=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@Hazztech","is_favorited":false,"timestamp":1398556800,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgzfMJYLAnDPB_QiRet4AaABAg.8Gc-w3ZyBvG8P90TXaH8vW","parent":"UgzfMJYLAnDPB_QiRet4AaABAg","text":"Quick Time Pro 7_kg is probs the name of the composer, or not, anyhow, there's a remade version by a guy called \"Andromeda\" titled \"Tits that fits\"","like_count":2,"author_id":"UCev1cjZBSZcEcAFDvG7O2bA","author":"@axelaquascorch3866","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_lxpO-Rwl5J9RpPv9AMJ30B1OnLSUh2cU0hnULKFhjJTw=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@axelaquascorch3866","is_favorited":false,"timestamp":1493251200,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgzfMJYLAnDPB_QiRet4AaABAg.8Gc-w3ZyBvG8ahXBZjS2sc","parent":"UgzfMJYLAnDPB_QiRet4AaABAg","text":"In days of old, cracked versions of things using key generators (hence the name keygen music) would often come with music composed by the hacker/group of hackers that would be their version of a trademark. It would play while the keygen program was running. \n\nQuick Time Pro 7 would be the software the keygen was made for (thats why there is _kg standing for keygen after it) and it is the name given to the song because there was usually no song info on the program that played it so there was no other way of identifying it. \n\nThis was happening even in the 80's and 90's and chiptune (what this and most other keygen music is) was used a lot around that time for games and such. Mind you, this is just the smaller form of \"hacking\" that is still around today after its predecessor that started in the 70's has mostly stopped being a thing. If you wonder what the predecessor is it is a competitive thing where hacker or hacker teams would create entire \"crack intros\" for cracked software. Comment is long enough already so here is a wikipedia link for it if you are interested, for all I know you couldn't care less and I am wasting my time thinking I am giving someone information they find interesting :D \nhttps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Crack_intro","like_count":2,"author_id":"UCrAKBfC0mFqh6vhPuUk068A","author":"@0MissPhoenix","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_kFXFkWSnA09HRccickvC9_B2F9k-phjIpFKL4kaFPzWg=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@0MissPhoenix","is_favorited":false,"timestamp":1524787200,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"UgydYpFK3jGZgDU1Mod4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"Thumbs up if you came here for LetherIceCream's HOI HOI HOI vid","like_count":0,"author_id":"UCy4klYoN0gaHTi_go0BkhcQ","author":"@BilboBagins98","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_mC-Tn0xUoTaV8_bKVAfrb58gd0tOjXCa-P67ke7w=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author_url":"https://www.youtube.com/@BilboBagins98","is_favorited":false,"timestamp":1367020800,"is_pinned":false},{"id":"Ugwg7yTFLUGIbrrZgDF4AaABAg","parent":"root","text":"CumMaster QuickTime Pro 70kg me trouxe aqui (y)","like_count":0,"author_id":"UCBRrDfwEcEJZMQkInFz-Xfw","author":"@bielcrazyjooj","author_thumbnail":"https://yt3.ggpht.com/ytc/AIdro_meURmW_iTblx-4dtPGbxt0OB_J23a2BrZL5U0aLpUg9VY=s88-c-k-c0x00ffffff-no-rj","author_is_uploader":false,"author